<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>下载</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/api.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/2_0/rem.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/2_0/util.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/fonts/duola_iconfont2.css"/>
    <style>
        .downloadPicture {
            width: 100%;
            height: 15.2rem;
            background: #C0C0C0;
        }

        .download-middle {
            height: 7.35rem;
            background: #FF3C54;
            box-shadow: 0px 3px 5px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.20);
            border: 1px solid #FF3C54;
        }

        .phone-container {
            margin: 1rem 1.75rem 1rem 1.55rem;
            height: 2.25rem;
        }

        .phone-container .phone {
            width: 2.25rem;
            height: 2.25rem;
            margin-right: 1rem;
            border-radius: 100%;
            background: #FF3C54;
            box-shadow: 0px 3px 7px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.20);
        }
        .phone-container .icon-weixin {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .phone-container .rightArrow {
            width: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-left: 0.2rem;
        }

        .input-container {
            height: 1.7rem;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ffffff;
            padding-bottom: 2px;
        }
        .input-container .number {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: Helvetica;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        .input-container input{
            color: #ffffff;
            display: block;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            padding-left: 0.2rem;
        }

        .code-container{
            margin-left: 4.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }

        .code-container input{
            width: 7rem;
            height: 1.7rem;
            line-height: 1.7rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 0.2rem;
            border: 1px solid #ffffff;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }

        .code-container .send-code{
            font-family: SourceHanSansCN-Normal;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            height: 1.4rem;
            width: 4.4rem;
            background: #262B30;
            box-shadow: 0px 3px 7px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.20);
            border-radius: 0.2rem;
        }

        .tip-container {
            background: #262B30;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-family: SourceHanSansCN-Light;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .download {
            width: 8.65rem;
            height: 1.7rem;
            line-height: 1.7rem;
            text-align: center;
            background: #FF3C54;
            box-shadow: 0px 3px 7px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.20);
            border-radius: 0.2rem;
        }

        .words {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            line-height: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="flex flex-vertical" style="height: 100%">
    <div class="downloadPicture"></div>
    <div class="download-middle">
        <div class="phone-container flex flex-center">
            <div class="phone flex flex-center">
                <i class="duola-iconfont icon-weixin"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="input-container flex-1 flex flex-bottom">
                <span class="number">+86|</span>
                <input type="tel" size="8"/>
            </div>
            <span class="duola-iconfont icon-weixin rightArrow"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="code-container flex flex-bottom">
            <input type="tel" />
            <div class="send-code flex flex-center"> 发送验证吗</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tip-container flex-1 flex flex-center">
        <div class="flex flex-center flex-vertical">
            <div class="download">下载多啦衣梦APP</div>
            <div class="words" >“在 多啦衣梦 天天换新衣真的让我无法自拔了 <br/> 现在加入有100RMB优惠券 <br/> 这种美事怎么能不拖着你一起来”</div>
            <div>穿衣从此不在买</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<script type="text/javascript" src="../script/api.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../script/url.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../script/doT_min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../script/uz.js"></script>
</body>
</html>